---
import Layout from '../../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout title="Privacy Policy">
  <head slot="head">
    <meta name="robots" content="noindex, nofollow" />
  </head>

  <div class="min-h-[80vh] flex justify-center p-4 md:p-12">
    <div class="max-w-4xl w-full space-y-8 animate-fade-in text-slate-300">
      <div class="border-b border-slate-800 pb-8">
        <h1 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-bold text-white mb-4">Privacy Policy</h1>
        <p class="text-slate-400">
          Transparency is important to me. Here I explain how this portfolio site processes data –
          especially regarding the integrated AI functions.
        </p>
      </div>

      <section class="space-y-4">
        <h2 class="text-xl font-bold text-emerald-400">1. Responsible Person</h2>
        <p>Responsible for data processing on this website is:</p>
        <div class="bg-slate-900/50 p-4 rounded-xl border border-slate-800">
          <p class="font-bold text-white">Sinan Uçar</p>
          <p class="mt-2 text-blue-400">Email: sinan@realizetogether.com</p>
        </div>
      </section>

      <section class="space-y-4">
        <h2 class="text-xl font-bold text-white">2. Hosting & Log Files</h2>
        <p>
          This website is hosted by external service providers (Vercel Inc. and Render). To deliver
          the site securely and stably, the host servers automatically collect information in
          so-called server log files (IP address, browser, time). This is done on the basis of Art.
          6 para. 1 lit. f GDPR (legitimate interest in secure provision).
        </p>
      </section>

      <section class="space-y-4">
        <div class="bg-blue-900/10 border border-blue-500/20 p-6 rounded-2xl">
          <h2 class="text-xl font-bold text-blue-400 mb-2">3. Use of Google Gemini API (AI)</h2>
          <p class="mb-4">
            This website offers interactive functions (chatbot, image analysis) supported by
            Artificial Intelligence.
          </p>
          <ul class="list-disc pl-5 space-y-2 text-sm">
            <li>
              <strong>Data Transfer:</strong> When you enter a message in the chat or upload an image
              for analysis, these inputs are sent to Google's API (Google Cloud / Vertex AI / Gemini)
              to generate a response.
            </li>
            <li>
              <strong>Processing in the USA:</strong> Google may process data in the USA. Google is certified
              under the "EU-US Data Privacy Framework," guaranteeing an adequate level of data protection.
            </li>
            <li>
              <strong>No Storage by Me:</strong> I do not permanently store your chat histories or uploaded
              images on my servers. The display occurs transiently in your browser (Local Storage).
            </li>
            <li>
              <strong>Note:</strong> Please do not enter sensitive personal data (health data, passwords,
              real names of third parties) into the chat.
            </li>
          </ul>
        </div>
      </section>

      <section class="space-y-4">
        <h2 class="text-xl font-bold text-white">4. Contacting</h2>
        <p>
          If you write to me via email or LinkedIn, your details will be stored by me for the
          purpose of processing the request. I will not pass on this data without your consent.
        </p>
      </section>

      <div class="pt-8 border-t border-slate-800">
        <a href="/en/" class="text-slate-500 hover:text-white transition-colors">← Back to Home</a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</Layout>
